data.title: Oliver H Mathewes, 717 Folly Road, Charleston, SC - Charleston Real Estate Agent
data.meta_description: Oliver  H Mathewes, 717 Folly Road, Charleston, SC - Charleston Real Estate Agent. Trust Carolina One Real Estate for the most complete listings in Charleston.
data.text: Oliver began his real estate career in 1980. Oliver is one of Carolina One Real Estate's top selling brokers. Not only is Oliver a professional, goal-driven selling broker, but he is also Broker Associate for Carolina One Real Estate's Commercial Division. Oliver's innate knowledge of the Charleston metro area allows him to find the best location for your business to succeed. Oliver also specializes in Estate and REO sales. Oliver has been able to help families achieve the dream of buying their own home. Over the past few years, Oliver has assisted many families to purchase a home through Estate sales and Bank REOs.
